<p>The mini-hub is made up of:</p> 
<ul>
<li><a href="/service-manual/styles-components-patterns/typography">heading and sub-heading</a> which sits at the top of the page</li>
<li><a href="/service-manual/styles-components-patterns/contents-list">contents list component</a> beneath the heading</li> 
